quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  47,10,"Baaxol ma-gexaana innaa keenik dumi marih ellecabo kah tekke inna yabloonuh? Yalli dabooqa keenil yiggiggileeh, bayseh, kaadu a koros wonnah tan digaala le"
  47,11,"Toh kah kinnim diggah Yalli yeemene marih awlaay, diggah koroosite mari awlah lem mali"
  47,12,"Diggah Yalli yeemeneeh meqe- taamoomi abe mara jannootay guba weeqaytitte kak gexxa culsa, koroosite marii hatkaanaah saqi elle yakme innal yakmen addunyal kaadu girá ken orbeyna"
  47,13,"Makiná magaala taniih, koo teyyeeqe ku-magaalak qandeh gibduk, ken finqisneeh cateyna malon"
  47,14,"Isi Rabbik baxxaqqâ bagul yan num kee, le-umá taama edde bilqisimte maray sinni kalbi- fayxiixa kataate maay missowta? mamissowta"
  47,15,"Yallak meesitá akah xagnisimte jannatih ceelallo, leek weeqaytittey carroote sinnii kee, canak weeqaytittey tami kak milaggootewaa elle tan, kaadu gocoyuy kas-mudewaak weeqaytittey yaaqube marah sattaa kee salfa-le elle tan, liyyuh yan malabay agle sinnik weeqaytitte elle tan. Kaadu usun ummaan caxâ mixuk qaynootaa kee sinni Rabbik dambi cabti elle lon. A jannatal yan mari, korosuy giral waartay, niqna kak caddok taturte lee yafqeeniy edde luk uluuqa kak targiggiqeh inna-lee (mali)"
  47,16,"Munaafiqhiinik koo ankacsa mari yan (nabiyow), ku-xaquk bukku iyyan waqdi qilmi kah yontocowwe marak iyyaanah, away iyyem macaay? Iyyan Toh Yalli sorkocobbaxitte kak alfeeh, sinni kalbi-fayxiixa kataate (katye) mara"
  47,17,"Tirri iyye marah Yalli tirto keenih osseeh, ken yallak-meesi keenih yeceeh tet keenih xabbacoyseh"
  47,18,"Qhiyaama garciik (hurubbaak) keenit tamaateemiksah qambaalaanam maay lon? Nummaak tet astooti (qalaamoota) keenih temeetehik, toysa maca keenih xiqaah usun aban kassit Qhiyaama tamaate waqdi"
  47,19,"Toysa ixig (nabiyow) ; diggah cakkil yaqbuden Yalli aneewaam inki Yallaksah. Kaadu nabiyow isee kee lab-moominiin kee say- moominiinih dambi-cabti esser isi Rabbil, Yalli sin angoyyii kee sin orbeyna yaaxigeh"
  47,20,"Yeemene mari jihaadal (koros gaadul) nee amrissa suura obsiminnay iyyan, tonnaluk qeebi elle cussuume suuray madqa kak karriqqa itta obta waqdii, sorkocobbaxittet biyak-le mari (munaafiqhiin kinnuk), rabi-qeero buulte numih wagittoh innah tanwagittoh koo fan wagitah ken table. Keenih taysem"
  47,21,"Yallih amri oggolaanaah, meqe maxcot yaabaanama. Amri yiggiriqqeeh, jihaad (gaadi) madqime waqdii munaafiqhiin tinqibeh, tokkel Yalla nummaysaanam diggah keenih aysukten Yallih amri cinaanamak"
  47,22,"Iimaanat derre cabteenih umaanet baaxó baysaah, sinni ramad yargiqe mara maay takken"
  47,23,"Toh Yalli abaareeh, aytiitaa kee intiita waysiise mara cakkik"
  47,24,Qhuraan ma-cubbusaana innaa hinnak ken sorkocobbaxittet koflitte tanniih (alifû taniih)
  47,25,"Diggah diinik korraaqeeh koroosannuh wadirih gace mari tirto keenih baxxaqimteek gamadal, sheetan ken umá-taama keenit bilqiseeh, anettoonuh uddur keenih yeyxeere"
  47,26,"Too badis keenit kah yekkem, diggah usun Yalli oobisem (qhuraan) yinqibe marak (koros kinnuk) amrittek-tu siinik oggolenno iyyeenimih sabbata. Yalli ken sirritte yaaxigeh"
  47,27,"Ken caalat mannaay, malayka coori keenik tayyaaqe waqdi ken foocittee kee ken saloofa aagaruk"
  47,28,"Too digaala ken kah geytem diggaluk usun Yalla tanqibisem (tayneeqebem) kattaateeniih, kay kacni edde yanim yinqibeenimî sabbata, edde luk Yalli ken meqe taamoomi bayseh"
  47,29,Hinnak sorkocobbaxittet biyak kak yan mari (munaafiqhiin kinnuk) Yalli ken bagi-umaaneena ayyaaqe weelem yekkelee
  47,30,"Kaadu faxinninoy (nabiyow) ken koo ayballayuk neneeh, ken astootil ken aaxaguk ten. Kaadu Yalli xiibitak iyyeh; maxcok obsal (saaqiyyol) ken aaxigettooh. Yalli sin taamoomi yaaxigeh"
  47,31,Xiibitah an sin aqiyyirennoomul (mokkorennomul) siinik giclo abáa kee yasbire mara ixiggi haynam fan kaadu sin taamoomi mokkorenno
  47,32,"Diggah koroositeeh, Yallih gitak sinam waaseeh, Yallih farmoyta yekeelefeeh kaah sadu yekke mari tirto keenih baxxaqimteek geeral, Yallak tu-makalaanaay, ken taamoomi Yalli baysele"